comments: Simons (POR) is established in front of Doncic (DAL) and absorbs the contact as Doncic backs him down during his post-dribble.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Lillard's (POR) driving shot attempt.
Finney-Smith (DAL) moves alongside Lillard's (POR) path as incidental contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Grant (POR) is last to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds. DAL receives possession of the ball.
Simons (POR) inbounds the ball within the five seconds allotted to POR.
Lillard (POR) and Bullock (DAL) engage and immediately disengage in arm contact off-ball during the inbound.
Dinwiddie (DAL) moves alongside Grant's (POR) path and maintains a legal guarding position as during the driving shot attempt.
Grant (POR) does not maintain a legal guarding position as he moves laterally into Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and initiates body contact, which affects his SQBR during his drive.
Bullock (DAL) reaches in and initiates contact with Lillard's (POR) arm prior to his upward shooting motion.
Hart (POR) attempts to commit a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Little (POR) moves alongside Doncic (DAL) during his drive and absorbs the incidental contact as Doncic loses his footing.
Simons (POR) commits a take foul on Hardaway Jr. (DAL).
Simons (POR) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
